                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 24.588,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 127101,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in No. 73-762, Sosna against Iowa, and the judgment and opinion of the Court in 73-1313, ITT against the International Brotherhood of Electrical Workers Union will each be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 24.588,
                        "stop": 143.14,
